<summary>Example Solution</summary>

```elixir
defmodule Stack do
  use GenServer

  @impl true
  def init(state) do
    {:ok, state}
  end

  @impl true
  def handle_call(:pop, _from, state) do
    [head | tail] = state
    {:reply, head, tail}
  end

  @impl true
  def handle_call({:push, element}, _from, state) do
    new_state = [element | state]
    {:reply, new_state, new_state}
  end
end
```

</details>

